<p>Oh dear! 'Ah, yeah, yeah it was Julia Morris. And didn't she make the most amazing pink kitten? She was just so fabulous in that costume,' Chappel said on the show</p>

<p>'Ah, yeah, yeah it was Julia Morris. And didn't she make the most amazing pink kitten? She was just so fabulous in that costume,' Chappel said on the show.</p>

